title: Hour 1 - NFL Week 1 Reaction, Ross Tucker
itunes:title: Hour 1 - NFL Week 1 Reaction, Ross Tucker
description:
Dan and the Danettes are relishing the first Monday of the football season ad react to all of yesterday's action. And NFL insider Ross Tucker stops by to wonder at the fact that the NFL still allows ties to occur.
